node.text:
Got a chance to get a great back day workout in with my first time using @jsculptfitness fitness belt! Some workouts I wear a sweat belt, some I use a power lift belt, this day I had the benefit of both with this fitness belt. ITS NOT A WAIST TRAINER! You actually have to put in work to make your life change not some gimmick waist trainer, no small waist and fat face! 
Check out how much support I had on this back day, went crazy and even lifted my heaviest 500lbs without a power lift belt from having great back support. 
Burned tons of muffin top fat up under this belt at the same time. Head on over to @jsculptfitness and grab yours in all sizes 
And use

RYAN20
20% off "Original" JSCULPT fitness belt

#9MAG
